  "eventTitle": "Volunteer Orientation & Training Workshop",
  "eventDescription": "Join us for a comprehensive orientation and training program for new volunteers. Learn about Help Ukraine's mission, programs, and best practices for volunteering. This workshop covers volunteer rights and responsibilities, cultural sensitivity training, COVID-19 safety protocols, and hands-on experience with our tools and systems.",
  
